'''灰嬰症候群'''，或稱'''灰嬰症'''及'''灰嬰綜合徵'''，是一種初生嬰兒在接受靜脈注射[[氯黴素|氯黴素]]後出現的罕見嚴重副作用。<ref name=McIntyre_2004>{{cite journal | author = McIntyre J, Choonara I | title = Drug toxicity in the neonate. | journal = Biol Neonate | volume = 86 | issue = 4 | pages = 218-21 | year = 2004 | id = PMID 15249753}}</ref>

== 病理 ==
初生嬰兒由於並未能完全自行建立體內的[[酶|酶]]，尤其是[[肝臟|肝臟]]負責[[代謝|代謝]]的酶，去處理或分解身體內多餘的[[氯黴素|氯黴素]]，就會出此種情況。<ref name=Piñeiro-Carrero_2004>{{cite journal | author = Piñeiro-Carrero V, Piñeiro E | title = Liver. | journal = Pediatrics | volume = 113 | issue = 4 Suppl | pages = 1097-106 | year = 2004 | id = PMID 15060205}}</ref>

== 臨床徵狀 ==
當接受氯黴素後的2-9天，毒素積聚會出現以下徵狀：
*[[嘔吐|嘔吐]]
*[[皮膚|皮膚]]呈灰白色
*四肢無力
*[[低血壓|低血壓]]
*[[發紺|發紺]]（嘴唇及皮膚呈紫藍色）
*[[體溫過低|體溫過低]]
*[[心血管虛脫|心血管虛脫]]

== 治療 ==
[[氯黴素|氯黴素]]的治療必須立即停止，有可能需要進行[[等量換血|等量換血]]以去除體內的氯黴素。

== 預防 ==
灰嬰症候群可以在控制[[氯黴素|氯黴素]]的劑量及監察血液水平來避免。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Feder H | title = Chloramphenicol: what we have learned in the last decade. | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_southern-medical-journal_1986-09_79_9/page/1129 | journal = South Med J | volume = 79 | issue = 9 | pages = 1129-34 | year = 1986 | id = PMID 3529436}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Mulhall A, de Louvois J, Hurley R | title = Chloramphenicol toxicity in neonates: its incidence and prevention. | journal = Br Med J (Clin Res Ed) | volume = 287 | issue = 6403 | pages = 1424-7 | year = 1983 | id = PMID 6416440 | url=http://www.pubmedcentral.nih.gov/articlerender.fcgi?tool=pubmed&pubmedid=6416440 | format=Scanned copy & PDF}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Forster J, Hufschmidt C, Niederhoff H, Künzer W | title = Need for the determination of chloramphenicol levels in the treatment of bacterial-purulent meningitis with chloramphenicol succinate in infants and small children | journal = Monatsschr Kinderheilkd | volume = 133 | issue = 4 | pages = 209-13 | year = 1985 | id = PMID 4000136}}</ref>

